---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Tratamiento Médico Integral PAIPER | Artricenter — Reumatología Personalizada en CDMX"
  description="Modelo de tratamiento reumatológico integral: diagnóstico preciso con tecnología de alta especialidad, tratamiento personalizado y seguimiento clínico continuo para controlar tu enfermedad reumática."
  currentPage="/tratamiento-medico-integral"
  jsonLd={{
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "MedicalWebPage",
    "name": "Tratamiento Médico Integral PAIPER - Artricenter",
    "description": "Modelo de atención médica innovador para el diagnóstico y tratamiento integral de enfermedades reumáticas.",
    "url": "https://artricenter.com.mx/tratamiento-medico-integral",
    "about": {
      "@type": "MedicalTherapy",
      "name": "PAIPER - Programa de Atención Integral para Pacientes con Enfermedades Reumáticas",
      "description": "Programa de Atención Integral para Pacientes con Enfermedades Reumáticas (PAIPER). Tratamiento médico integral con diagnóstico preciso, ajustes terapéuticos personalizados y seguimiento clínico continuo."
    }
  }}
>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <!-- Diagnóstico -->
    <section id="diagnostico" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-20">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="sr-only">Tratamiento Médico Integral PAIPER — Artricenter</h1>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-6">Diagnóstico</h2>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-6">
          <div class="h-1 w-40 rounded-full" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgb(0, 83, 161))"></div>
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full animate-pulse" style="background-color: rgb(0, 83, 161)"></div>
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full" style="background-color: rgb(83, 175, 49)"></div>
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full" style="background-color: rgb(242, 144, 88)"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="h-1 w-40 rounded-full" style="background: linear-gradient(to left, transparent, rgb(242, 144, 88))"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">

          <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              En esta fase <strong class="text-blue-600">Artricenter</strong> realiza la evaluación médica exhaustiva de los pacientes y el diagnóstico de las enfermedades reumáticas. Aquí nuestros médicos determinan si la persona es candidata a tomar nuestro Tratamiento Médico Integral.
            </p>

            <p>
              En Artricenter contamos con equipos de alta tecnología, así como un cuerpo de médicos altamente calificados que garantizan un diagnóstico exacto, oportuno y confiable.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <div class="rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
            <img
              src="/assets/images/specialties/doctor-explaining.avif"
              alt="Médico reumatólogo explicando diagnóstico a paciente en Artricenter"
              class="w-full h-auto"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Separator -->
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-6 my-16">
      <div class="h-1 w-40 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-full"></div>
      <div class="flex gap-2">
        <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-blue-600 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
        <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="h-1 w-40 bg-gradient-to-l from-transparent via-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-full"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Tratamiento Médico Integral -->
    <section id="paiper" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-20">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-6 text-center">PAIPER</h2>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-6 mb-12">
          <div class="h-1 w-40 rounded-full" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgb(0, 83, 161))"></div>
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full animate-pulse" style="background-color: rgb(0, 83, 161)"></div>
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full" style="background-color: rgb(83, 175, 49)"></div>
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full" style="background-color: rgb(242, 144, 88)"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="h-1 w-40 rounded-full" style="background: linear-gradient(to left, transparent, rgb(242, 144, 88))"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          <p class="text-lg">
            El <strong class="text-blue-600">Programa de Atención Integral para Pacientes con Enfermedades Reumáticas (PAIPER)</strong> es un modelo de atención médica innovador y científicamente sustentado.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg">
            Su propósito es lograr el control efectivo de la enfermedad para elevar la calidad de vida de nuestros pacientes, garantizando resultados certeros sin comprometer su salud general.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-10">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-6 text-center">¿Cómo funciona nuestro modelo?</h3>
          </div>

          <p class="text-lg">
            Nuestro sistema opera a través de un <strong class="text-blue-600">tratamiento médico integral de 7 pasos</strong>, diseñado estratégicamente para ofrecer un beneficio real y duradero. Gracias a este enfoque integral, el paciente obtiene:
          </p>

          <div class="space-y-4 mt-8">
            <div class="paiper-step flex gap-4 items-start">
              <div class="step-number w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg shadow-lg">1</div>
              <div class="step-line w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-600 to-blue-300 self-stretch"></div>
              <p class="step-text text-lg flex items-center">
                Programa de consultas médicas
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="paiper-step flex gap-4 items-start">
              <div class="step-number w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg shadow-lg">2</div>
              <div class="step-line w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-600 to-blue-300 self-stretch"></div>
              <p class="step-text text-lg flex items-center">
                Programa de educación, promoción y prevención para las enfermedades reumáticas
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="paiper-step flex gap-4 items-start">
              <div class="step-number w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg shadow-lg">3</div>
              <div class="step-line w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-600 to-blue-300 self-stretch"></div>
              <p class="step-text text-lg flex items-center">
                Programa de estudios de laboratorio e imagenología
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="paiper-step flex gap-4 items-start">
              <div class="step-number w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg shadow-lg">4</div>
              <div class="step-line w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-600 to-blue-300 self-stretch"></div>
              <p class="step-text text-lg flex items-center">
                Programa farmacológico
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="paiper-step flex gap-4 items-start">
              <div class="step-number w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg shadow-lg">5</div>
              <div class="step-line w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-600 to-blue-300 self-stretch"></div>
              <p class="step-text text-lg flex items-center">
                Programa nutricional
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="paiper-step flex gap-4 items-start">
              <div class="step-number w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg shadow-lg">6</div>
              <div class="step-line w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-600 to-blue-300 self-stretch"></div>
              <p class="step-text text-lg flex items-center">
                Programa de rehabilitación
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="paiper-step flex gap-4 items-start">
              <div class="step-number w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg shadow-lg">7</div>
              <div class="step-line w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-600 to-blue-300 self-stretch"></div>
              <p class="step-text text-lg flex items-center">
                Programa orientación telefónica
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <style is:global>
    /* Animación escalonada estilo Remotion para los 7 pasos PAIPER */
    @keyframes paiper-number-in {
      0% {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: scale(0) rotate(-180deg);
      }
      60% {
        transform: scale(1.2) rotate(10deg);
      }
      100% {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: scale(1) rotate(0deg);
      }
    }

    @keyframes paiper-line-draw {
      0% {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: scaleY(0);
        transform-origin: top;
      }
      100% {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: scaleY(1);
        transform-origin: top;
      }
    }

    @keyframes paiper-text-slide {
      0% {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateX(-30px);
      }
      100% {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateX(0);
      }
    }

    @keyframes paiper-glow {
      0%, 100% {
        box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 83, 161, 0.5);
      }
      50% {
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 83, 161, 0.8), 0 0 30px rgba(0, 83, 161, 0.4);
      }
    }

    .paiper-step {
      opacity: 1;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
      transform-origin: center;
      border-radius: 0.75rem;
      padding: 0.75rem;
      cursor: default;
    }

    .paiper-step:hover {
      transform: scale(1.03);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 83, 161, 0.15);
      background-color: rgba(0, 83, 161, 0.03);
    }

    .paiper-step .step-number {
      opacity: 0;
      animation: paiper-number-in 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1) forwards,
                 paiper-glow 2s ease-in-out infinite 0.6s;
    }

    .paiper-step .step-line {
      opacity: 0;
      animation: paiper-line-draw 0.4s ease-out forwards;
    }

    .paiper-step .step-text {
      opacity: 0;
      animation: paiper-text-slide 0.5s ease-out forwards;
    }

    /* Staggered delays for each step - CSS only */
    .paiper-step:nth-child(1) .step-number,
    .paiper-step:nth-child(1) .step-line,
    .paiper-step:nth-child(1) .step-text {
      animation-delay: calc(0.2s + var(--base-delay, 0s));
    }

    .paiper-step:nth-child(2) .step-number,
    .paiper-step:nth-child(2) .step-line,
    .paiper-step:nth-child(2) .step-text {
      animation-delay: calc(0.4s + var(--base-delay, 0s));
    }

    .paiper-step:nth-child(3) .step-number,
    .paiper-step:nth-child(3) .step-line,
    .paiper-step:nth-child(3) .step-text {
      animation-delay: calc(0.6s + var(--base-delay, 0s));
    }

    .paiper-step:nth-child(4) .step-number,
    .paiper-step:nth-child(4) .step-line,
    .paiper-step:nth-child(4) .step-text {
      animation-delay: calc(0.8s + var(--base-delay, 0s));
    }

    .paiper-step:nth-child(5) .step-number,
    .paiper-step:nth-child(5) .step-line,
    .paiper-step:nth-child(5) .step-text {
      animation-delay: calc(1.0s + var(--base-delay, 0s));
    }

    .paiper-step:nth-child(6) .step-number,
    .paiper-step:nth-child(6) .step-line,
    .paiper-step:nth-child(6) .step-text {
      animation-delay: calc(1.2s + var(--base-delay, 0s));
    }

    .paiper-step:nth-child(7) .step-number,
    .paiper-step:nth-child(7) .step-line,
    .paiper-step:nth-child(7) .step-text {
      animation-delay: calc(1.4s + var(--base-delay, 0s));
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
